Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:47.60,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}那時候的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:51.34,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}對著無法起飛的螺旋槳做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.80,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}朝著天空的另一半抬頭望去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.91,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}光著腳丫肆意奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:03.35,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我們永遠都是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:10.44,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}無論誤會與否 就是對生活充滿自信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:23.79,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}如同把重要的寶物 藏起來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:32.39,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}再也無法發現那顆深藏起來的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:35.39,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}咕嚕咕嚕轉上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.50,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}用這根魔法之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:44.53,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}把眼淚和晴天混合起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:48.24,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}怕寂寞的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.44,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}夢想一定會實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:59.77,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我們要永遠在一起哦
